Class Flat

java.lang.Object
sg.edu.ntu.sc2002.ay2425.fcsdGroup2.model.entities.Flat
public class Flat extends Object
Represents a flat (unit) within a residential block. Contains information about floor number, unit number, booking status, type, and block.
